# Tera Template Syntax Guide

## Variable Substitution

{% raw %}
```tera
{{ variable_name }}
```
{% endraw %}

## Filters

{% raw %}
```tera
{{ variable_name | filter_name }}
{{ name | snake }}
{{ text | upper }}
```
{% endraw %}

## Conditionals

{% raw %}
```tera
{% if condition %}
  Content if true
{% else %}
  Content if false
{% endif %}
```
{% endraw %}

## Loops

{% raw %}
```tera
{% for item in array %}
  {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
```
{% endraw %}

### Loop Variables

- `loop.index` - 1-based index
- `loop.index0` - 0-based index
- `loop.first` - True if first iteration
- `loop.last` - True if last iteration
- `loop.length` - Total items

## Comments

{% raw %}
```tera
{# This comment won't appear in output #}
```
{% endraw %}

## Advanced Features

### Set Variables

{% raw %}
```tera
{% set my_var = some_value %}
{{ my_var }}
```
{% endraw %}

### Include Templates

{% raw %}
```tera
{% include "other_template.tera" %}
```
{% endraw %}

### Inheritance

{% raw %}
```tera
{% extends "base.tera" %}

{% block content %}
  Custom content
{% endblock %}
```
{% endraw %}
